+ Youth Of Freedom +;-;GAMEPLAY : 10/10 Team Fotress 2 is an critically acclaim shooter that takes some of its formular from a fast-paced games such as Quake & Unreal Tournament. It is considered to be one of the best free 2 play games ever made next to Dota 2. Did i not mentioned that these two games is published by Valve ? Yup anything that Valve made is a masterpiece. The game had a total of nine classes. Ranging from sniper,demoman,scout,heavy,engineer,soldier,pyro,medic & spy. Each of the classes had their own role and different play style. Each of the classes had their own charming personality and likeable characteristics. You can also taunt to kill your enemy if you are lucky. The games provide a massive tons of modes and it rare to see in a first person shooter game. Just look at these list : http://wiki.teamfortress.com/wiki/List_of_game_modes You get numerous weapon,different parts of outfits as you play through many matches. There is also a crafting system where you combined different parts of weapon & scrap to obtained a much more powerful weapon. Each of the weapon provides different types of ability & stats. Most of it have their own pros & cons. The game requires a lot of teamwork sometimes depending on what modes you are playing. Also medic + heavy = OWNAGE. GRAPHICS : 10/10 For a game that come out in 2007,it age extremely well and still to these days the cartoonish artstyle impress me a lot. A lot of the texture are well details as well as the character models. Each of the maps provide different variety of background & well thought out level design. The animations perform from each character are well done and doesn't look like crap. This game also have blood & gore in it too and it is pretty well detailed too. AUDIO : 10/10 The soundtrack for this game is superb especially the main theme songs. All of them are done in an orchestral theme. While they don't go for a realistic sound effects since it doesn't fit in with the game theme,they go for a much more funny approach in making all of sound effects that really blend in with the feels of the games. The voice acting for each of the classes is excellent ( except for pyro cause he mostly mumble random stuff ). Each of them have their own unique taunts & quote. LONG-LASTING APPEAL : 10/10 This games provides more modes than any first person shooter game does along with an on-going update with every 2-3 weeks or so. There is a huge amount of items you collect during your gameplay sessions. Not to mentioned there is a bunch of custom map that you download & play on. It even much more fun if you have friends to play with you adding a ton of enjoyment into the game. You will never get bored with each of the class since there is always a challenge when dealing with certain type of situation. Not to mentioned the amount of achievement you can get just by playing the game is huge so this will keep you busy for a long times. FINAL VERDICT : 10/10 Really recommended for everyone especially to those who are not a fan of first person shooter game. Every game that Valve made have their own special moments,innovative gameplay & unique style. A truly masterpiece of arts. GRADE : S ( Masterpiece )
