FUNKe;-;A Shooter that ages and adapts at its own pace. For people experienced in Military-esque shooters like CoD or Battlefield, This game will require you to completely throw out the ideas of those games in favor of more unique gameplay elements aswell as teamwork being much more essential than in your standard shooter. TF2 is layered in multiple games within it's core shooter design. For collectors, you can get potentially hundreds or thousands of a specific item, and even potentially wield a collectors variant of it. For fashionistas you can design and paint your character as you see fit. For shooters you can ignore it all and focus on playing. Even amist the heat of battle, your enemy could become your best friend seconds later. Say you're looking down a hall. you see a soldier. You blink. There's a pyro now too. You blink. The soldier is now dancing the conga. The pyro is now too. You run up to them and dance aswell. Blink. Both teams are now crowded in a room raving. Before you know it you're headbutting and hifiving that sniper who kept headshotting you minutes ago. In a nutshell: Why haven't you downloaded this yet?
