uy a ticket and do tours, everyone's after the fabelled "Australium weapons", which are golden weapons that go for alot of money, so if your willing to have RNG hate or love you, try it out in conclusion, TF2 has so much things modern day FPS's don't have, if you haven't tried TF2 yet, what are you doing? it's free, forever, GO DOWNLOAD IT MAGGOT!!
