Refractal;-;As you can tell by my play time I quite enjoy this game. I find it extremely fun. This game is filled with the craziest things. You can grab your minigun, or your sheild and sword. It has nine classes to chose from, all with distinct roles and weapon sets. What is really cool is that it is fun even to the free players. You can get most weapons without having to pay. If you decide to buy anything from the in-game store you are automatically upgraded to a premium account. All you gain from this is more frequent item drops, the ability to trade and other minor things. All in all I think the game is extremely entertaining.
