| AF | Knilax;-;Summary: 9/10 A superb online Free-To-Play experience you and your friends will spend countless hours playing. Details: It has the standard Free-To-Play microtransactions, sure, but it is and shall remain my favorite shooter of all time. Why? The unique classes. The classes differenciate in lots of ways; some being more drastic then others. Including the Engineer who can build sentry guns, dispencers, and teleporters. Or the Spy, who can disguise as an enemy teammate and backstab them. Literally.
